data.value:
==============================Fixed Frequency============================ - This setting is for user to choose their own beat pattern and power. User need to enter Laser 1's wavelength and beat pattern value in GHz.
- 'Power' cannot be set separately as it suppose not to for OHS.
- Once set everything, Enable laser with 'Enable' button. User can check status with 'Status update' button.
- 'Save data' button will save and extract current data to excel file.

data.name: richTextBox2.Text
data.value:
============================== Connect =============================== - You need to connect two different COM port of unit. Please select correct COM port for each laser with 'Connect' button
- 'Device information' section will display each laser's capability
==============================CW Setting ============================= - This setting is for user to choose their own wavelength and power. It will calculate and create beat pattern as user have set.
- 'Power' cannot be set separately as it suppose not to for OHS.
- Once set everything, Enable laser with 'Enable' button. User can check status with 'Status update' button.
- 'Save data' button will save and extract current data to excel file.
